  "body": "<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/43170ec70307413fcd326cff227fa6b1c6a6036c_0.webp\" alt=\"Create: Access Denied - Simple access management for your networks.\" width=\"100%\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/7bfd9ede8da9adc1a1d2040db888e6b4f03070fb_0.webp\" alt=\"Control access from a simple interface. Shift-click to remove a player. Type username and click the plus icon to add a player.\" width=\"100%\">\n<a href=\"https://github.com/5w14/create-access-denied\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/c737b005a946748fc278824b23ec4dc9a43fc153_0.webp\" width=\"49.7%\" alt=\"Github - Issuess & Source Code\"></a> <a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/fw14\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/c476f7e6f09d2bdd412f0235fa2c53dc8a2ad34c_0.webp\" width=\"49.73%\" alt=\"Ko-fi - Support\"></a><br>\n\n<br>\n\n<details>\n<summary>Text-based description</summary>\n\n# Create: Access Denied\n> Simple access management for your networks.\n\nControl access to a logistics network from a simple interface: \n - Shift-click a player's face to remove access \n - Type in a username and click the plus button to give access \n\n[Issues & Source Code on GitHub](https://github.com/5w14/create-access-denied)\n\n[Support me on Ko-Fi](https://github.com/5w14/create-access-denied)\n\n</details>\n\n",
